ol.li: User sets EAX=syscall#, args in EBX/ECX/EDX
int 0x80 triggers IDT gate (must have DPL=3)
CPU switches to kernel stack via TSS.ESP0
CPU pushes SS, ESP, EFLAGS, CS, EIP onto kernel stack
Handler saves remaining registers, dispatches syscall
iret restores SS, ESP, EFLAGS, CS, EIP
User resumes at Ring 3 with EAX=result

div.p: EAX = 2 (SYS_WRITE) EBX = 1 (fd) ECX = buffer_ptr EDX = count
